## Features
 
- **Add transactions** — log income and expenses with name, amount, category, and date
- **Real-time balance** — net balance, total income, and total expenses update instantly
- **Expense breakdown** — visual category bars showing where your money goes
- **Filter transactions** — view all, income only, or expenses only
- **Persistent data** — transactions saved to `localStorage`, survive page reloads
- **Live stock ticker** — real-time prices for BTC, ETH, MSFT, NVDA, AAPL, TSLA, META, and more via TradingView
- **Market news feed** — live financial news in the right panel via TradingView
- **Light / Dark mode** — theme toggle that also updates the TradingView widgets
- **Fully responsive** — works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
 
