## Getting Started
 
No build tools or dependencies required. Just open the file.
 
```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Rafaz01/Finance-Dashboard-1.git
 
# Open in your browser
open index.html
```
 
Or simply download the ZIP and open `index.html` in any modern browser.
 
